rdLife物种一览表：Burhinus oedicnemus Lepage, D. Burhinus oedicnemus. Avibase: The world bird database. Bird Studies Canada. 2004 （英语）. 互聯網鳥類收藏上有关Stone-curlew的錄像、照片和音頻", "shortSummary": "歐亞石鴴（学名：Burhinus oedicnemus）是石鴴科各物種當中分佈於最北方的一種。《中国鸟类名录10.0版》将欧石鸻中文名恢复为石鸻。 歐亞石鴴在石鴴科類算是偏中型的水鳥，長度約38至46公分，翼展約76至88公分，重量約290至535克。其有一個黃黑色的鳥喙，大的…", "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Burhinus_oedicnemus_insularum_Lanzarote_1.jpg/960px-Burhinus_oedicnemus_insularum_Lanzarote_1.jpg", "order": "Charadriiformes", "family": "Burhinidae", "genus": "Burhinus", "species": "Burhinus oedicnemus", "orderCn": "鸻形目", "familyCn": "石鸻科", "genusCn": "石鸻属", "speciesCn": "石鸻", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "orderId": "taxonomy-order-charadriiformes", "familyId": "taxonomy-family-burhinidae", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-burhinus", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-burhinus-oedicnemus", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "order": "taxonomy-order-charadriiformes", "family": "taxonomy-family-burhinidae", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-burhinus", "species": "taxonomy-species-burhinus-oedicnemus"}, "expandable": true, "x": -967.16, "y": 277.61, "z": -119.46}], "links": [{"key": "bird-歐石鴴-54014d9d__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-burhinus-oedicnemus", "source": "bird-歐石鴴-54014d9d", "target": "taxonomy-species-burhinus-oedicnemus", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-burhinus-oedicnemus__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-burhinus", "source": "taxonomy-species-burhinus-oedicnemus", "target": "taxonomy-genus-burhinus", "relation": "belongs_to_genus", "label": "属于属", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：石鸻 属于属 石鸻属。"}]}
